The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, aconite
2 different pets are kept: cat, guinea-pig
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, parkour
1. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
3. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |
| Food          | pepper    | avocado      |
| Hobby         | writing   | baking       |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | martial-arts |
| Flower   | aconite  | dahlia    |
